headline.main: NEW ZEALAND SETS FOREIGN TRADE PLAN; Aims at Rigid War Pattern and Empire Stability

lead_paragraph: WELLINGTON, New Zealand, Oct. 4 -- A three-point foreign trade program revealing that New Zealand's overseas commerce is being rigidly confined within the war pattern has been announced by Commerce Minister Daniel Sulivan.
abstract: N Z: Min D Sullivan announces foreign trade plan
